text: I also excersie(mostly long walks), watch cycling and F1. I can agree that it's hard to balance(more so with school),so I just relax when I feel I have artblock.
Speaking of, how do you deal with artblock?

I ask myself that everyday, and I don't really have a straight answer for this one.
What I do try and do is focus on something else, try and break my patterns, like I said before, In most times it's just about perseverance, because if you wait for inspiration you'll never get to make anything :smiley:
